p: MEGA7.0 was used to analyze the variation of amino acid between cluster A and B in China, as well as reference clusters in Singapore, French Polynesia, and Malaysia. The structure of protein was modeled by Swiss-Model. [ 29] SuperPose Version 1.0 (University of Alberta, Canada) was used to compare the protein structures and get root mean squared deviations (RMSD) value. The structures are considered very similar when RMSD < 1.1 Å. [ 30]
